yir 0.1

resource cpu0 cpu
resource shader0 shader

cpu.const seed cpu0 4
cpu.const inc cpu0 3
cpu.add sum cpu0 seed inc
data.move sum_on_shader shader0 sum shader0
shader.dispatch shaded shader0 sum_on_shader
shader.print done shader0 shaded

edge dep seed sum
edge dep inc sum
edge xfer sum sum_on_shader
edge dep sum_on_shader shaded
edge dep shaded done
edge effect shaded done
